| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5964 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ee94bc1-509b-51f8-921e-8d613e854226"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
